			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "Budget ME! Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"Pretty Pipes is a mod which allows players to connect their chests and other storage options together to create a nice ecosystem which they can access easily and without too much issues."
				""
				"While you'll need pipes (lots of them) to start tinkering with this mod, you'll also need a wrench to properly control the pipes. With the Pipe Wrench you can do the following modifications:"
				""
				"- You can disconnect pipes from certain blocks as, by default, the pipes will connect to anything accessible for them."
				""
				"- By shift right-clicking a pipe, you can break them very easily."
				""
				"- If you're holding the Wrench in your right hand, and a block in your right hand, you can place the blocks from the right hand, as covers for the pipes. These covers can be removed by shift right-clicking them with the Wrench."
			]
			dependencies: ["606DD326CCAB7FB2"]
