			subtitle: "Food, Tools, Wires. All on the go: The Engineer's Toolbox  is used to store tools and other items. Right-clicking it will open it. Each slot can only store a specific type of item/block; \"Food\" can store edibles, \"Tools\" can store tools, \"Wiring\" can store Immersive Engineering coils and similar items, and \"Anything\" can store, as it sounds, any block or item.Shift right-clicking it will place it. It can be right-clicked in its block form to be opened. When broken, it will retain all of the items in it"
